00:19:54,815 --> 00:19:57,810
but even then, God prohibited only the meat.

227
00:19:57,810 --> 00:20:04,520
But twice in the Quran, God says "the idol worshipers say if God wills, we will not do this."

228
00:20:04,520 --> 00:20:05,915
So, they blame it on God.

229
00:20:05,915 --> 00:20:11,099
"I didn't get up for the Morning Prayer, Fajr, because God... if God wanted me to get up, I would have gotten up.

230
